## Collaboration & Data

Many of these projects involve collaborative research with colleagues across multiple institutions. When possible, replication materials are made available through journal repositories or the [Harvard Dataverse](https://dataverse.harvard.edu/).

For questions about ongoing research or potential collaboration, please feel free to [contact me](mailto:areeves@wustl.edu).

